<body>
  <main>
    <h1>Refund Policy</h1>

    <h5>1. Return Eligibility</h5>
    <ul>
      <li>Returns accepted within 30 days of delivery</li>
      <li>Item must be unused and in original packaging</li>
      <li>Proof of purchase required</li>
    </ul>

    <h5>2. Non-Refundable Items</h5>
    <ul>
      <li>Customized or hot-swapped modified keyboards</li>
      <li>Used switches or keycaps</li>
      <li>Final sale or clearance items</li>
    </ul>

    <h5>3. Refund Process</h5>
    <ol>
      <li>Contact support to initiate return</li>
      <li>Ship item back as instructed</li>
      <li>Inspection and refund within 7–10 business days</li>
    </ol>

    <h5>4. Shipping Fees</h5>
    <p>
      Return shipping is the customer’s responsibility unless the product
      is defective or incorrect.
    </p>

    <h5>5. Damaged or Defective Products</h5>
    <p>Report within 7 days of delivery for replacement or refund.</p>

    <h5>6. Late or Missing Refunds</h5>
    <p>
      Please contact your bank or payment provider before reaching out to
      us.
    </p>
  </main>
</body>
